      "firm_id": "optimistic_8",
      "description": "Looking for a rewarding project or a great source for parts? This vehicle is in poor condition and will need some serious TLC to get back on the road, but it's a fantastic opportunity for a mechanic or a hobbyist looking for their next big challenge! It\u2019s priced to sell and ready for someone with the right skills to give it a second life.",
