    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good, reliable condition and has been well-maintained throughout its life. The exterior is clean with only minor surface scratches and small stone chips consistent with regular use, while the interior remains comfortable and functional with some light wear on the driver's seat bolster. Mechanically, the car performs well, having received regular oil changes and service, making it a dependable choice for its next owner. It offers a great balance of quality and value for someone looking for a solid, honest vehicle.",
